  stimulus_text = 'In 1999, the city of Seattle, Washington, made history when it became the first major city in the United States to ban the use of plastic bags at checkout. This policy, which has since been adopted by many other cities, has been credited with reducing the amount of plastic waste in Seattle. However, some businesses and residents still express concerns about the policy, arguing that it ______ creates an unnecessary burden on consumers.',
